QuestData.Title: Seeing Where Your Loyalties Lie
QuestData.Description: Thar be just one thing...$b$bYancey hears things. A few o' me hearties were pretty deep in their cups when they told me about some $r $c that came a-rollin' through the Southern Command lookin' for charts and orders. Even ran a couple o' good pirates through, $g he: she; did.$b$bLike I said, they were up to their eyeballs in grog, but still... a buccaneer's gotta trust his ears. So I've just got one small task for ye, one sent down from Firallon hisself...$b$bBring me the head of Fleet Master Seahorn.
QuestData.LogDescription: Obtain the Head of Fleet Master Seahorn in Booty Bay.
QuestData.CompletionText: Firallon special-ordered this one himself. Said the tauren's too much of a risk.
QuestData.RewardText: Well blow me down! Now there's something ya don't see too often.$b$b<Yancey reaches out and shakes your hand.>$b$bWelcome aboard, $n. Plunder and booty await ye.
